import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react'; import { useLocation, useParams } from 'react-router-dom'; import { Container, Form, Table } from 'react-bootstrap'; import { getAllManager, getListTasksById } from '../../api/Task'; import { getEmployeeById } from '../../api/Employee'; import HeaderComponent from '../../components/Header'; const EmployeeInf = () => { const state = useLocation().state const [tasks, setTasks] = useState([]) const [data, setData] = useState([]) useEffect(() => { getEmployeeById(state.id).then(res => setData(res)).catch(err => console.log(err)) },[]) useEffect(() => { getAllManager(state.id).then(res => setTasks(res.data)).catch(err => console.log(err)) },[]) const row = tasks.map((task,index) => ( {task.name} {task.description} {task.deadline} {task.managerName} {task.ProductLine} {task.Model} {task.Type} {task.Capacity} {task.RatedCoolingCap} {task.Dimension} {task.RunningCurrent} {task.RatedPowerInput} {task.PowerSupply} {task.AirFlow} {task.Ext.StaticPressure} {task.RatedCOP} {task.Refrigerant} {task.Noise} {task.Weight} {task.LiquidPipe} {task.GasPipe} )) return ( <>
